dc_creator_sm: Department of Economic and Workforce Development ; City and Count of San Francisco
dc_description_s: The CityLots spatial data layer is a representation of the City and County of San Francisco's Subdivision parcels. Each of the 200,000-plus polygons has a unique BLKLOT identifier which is the Assessor Parcel Number (APN). Multiple level (condominium, live/work, et al.) lots are represented as well, with their ground or base lot being the MAPBLKLOT key.
dc_title_s: Enterprise Zone Lots, San Francisco, California, 2013
